性的成就是一种荣幸，我们只能希望继续创作音乐，与迄今为止聆听和支持我们的所有令人难以置信的人们建立联系。谢谢你！”</p><p>乐队主唱莫里斯向<a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-67646930" target="_blank" rel="noopener">BBC 广播电台 1</a>形容这一荣誉“有点像灵魂出窍”。她继续说道：“我们可以告诉我们的家人，他们会说，‘是的，这是相当大的。’”</p><p>乐队还表示，当他们前往布拉格参加演出时，他们在“德国的一个卡车停靠站”发现自己是获胜者。</p><p>梅兰告诉英国广播公司第一台：“我们几个人在里面试图购买格兰诺拉麦片和咖啡。然后我们就在雪地里跑来跑去，互相踢雨夹雪，尖叫着吓唬当地人。所以这是一声尖叫和一个拥抱，然后试图找到一些香槟。”</p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover/the-cover-the-last-dinner-party-interview-prelude-to-ecstasy-3552625"><em>《NME</em> 》《The Cover》的一次新采访</a>中，五人畅谈了他们目前的经历以及在音乐领域的崛起“感觉有点像开着一辆开得很快的汽车，却不再掌控方向盘” 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3552661" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3552661" style="width: 1990px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3552661" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/NME-COVER-THE-LAST-DINNER-PARTY-COVER-CREDIT-PHOEBE-FOX@1990x2488.jpg" alt="《最后的晚宴》 NME 封面" width="1990" height="2488" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/NME-COVER-THE-LAST-DINNER-PARTY-COVER-CREDIT-PHOEBE-FOX@1990x2488.jpg 1990w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/NME-COVER-THE-LAST-DINNER-PARTY-COVER-CREDIT-PHOEBE-FOX@1990x2488-400x500.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/NME-COVER-THE-LAST-DINNER-PARTY-COVER-CREDIT-PHOEBE-FOX@1990x2488-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/NME-COVER-THE-LAST-DINNER-PARTY-COVER-CREDIT-PHOEBE-FOX@1990x2488-696x870.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/NME-COVER-THE-LAST-DINNER-PARTY-COVER-CREDIT-PHOEBE-FOX@1990x2488-1392x1740.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/NME-COVER-THE-LAST-DINNER-PARTY-COVER-CREDIT-PHOEBE-FOX@1990x2488-1068x1335.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1990px) 100vw, 1990px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3552661" class="wp-caption-text"> NME 封面上的最后晚宴。图片来源：NME 的菲比·福克斯</figcaption></figure><p>莫里斯继续说道：“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-were-trying-to-ignore-the-words-hype-and-buzzy-band-3554464">我们试图忽略‘炒作’和‘热闹乐队’这些词</a>，只专注于我们的基础：演奏、创作和排练我们的音乐。”</p><p>后来，乐队触及了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-respond-to-industry-plant-allegations-nme-radar-3436536">他们是“工业工厂”的错误假设</a>。 “我们必须解决这个问题吗？”莫里斯向<em>NME</em>询问。戴维斯也表示：“我们认为这是一种恭维。如果人们认为这好得令人难以置信，那么我们只能说谢谢。”</p><p>在其他消息中，伦敦乐队和<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-radar/the-nme-100-essential-emerging-artists-for-2023-radar-3372061">NME 100</a>校友将于 2 月 2 日通过 Island 发行他们的首张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-announce-debut-album-prelude-to-ecstasy-release-new-single-on-your-side-listen-preorder-3528044">《Prelude To Ecstasy》</a> （<a href="https://tldp.lnk.to/preludetoecstasyPR" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预订</a>）。它将收录 2023 年的单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-shares-smashing-debut-single-nothing-matters-radar-3433299">《Nothing Matters》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-new-single-sinner-uk-tour-radar-3463558">《Sinner》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-share-new-single-my-lady-of-mercy-3511842">《My Lady Of Mercy》</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-announce-debut-album-prelude-to-ecstasy-release-new-single-on-your-side-listen-preorder-3528044#:~:text=The%20Last%20Dinner%20Party%20have,%2Fpre%2Dsave%20here).">《On Your Side》</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-announce-intimate-variety-show-at-london-roundhouse-buy-tickets-3507689">他们将在首张专辑发行前夕（2 月 1 日）在伦敦 Roundhouse 举办一场头条秀</a>。该团体此前曾开玩笑说，这场演出“可能是历史性的”。 <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fthe-last-dinner-party-tickets%2Fartist%2F5395177" target="_blank" rel="noopener">您可以在这里找到任何剩余的门票</a>。</p><p>然后他们将前往英国唱片店进行一系列演出，然后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-last-dinner-party-announce-2024-european-tour-dates-buy-tickets-3531799">开始欧洲巡演</a>。此外，乐队还将在巴塞罗那和波尔图的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/primavera-sound-announce-stacked-line-up-for-2024-3545261">Primavera Sound</a> 、比利时的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/foo-fighters-and-dua-lipa-announced-as-rock-werchter-2024-headliners-3537761">Rock Werchter</a>和苏格兰的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/trnsmt-2024-liam-gallagher-gerry-cinmamon-calvin-harris-lead-line-up-3545593">TRNSMT</a>演出。</p><p>与此同时，The Last Evening Party 还为<em>NME</em>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-cover">“The Cover”</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/check-out-the-last-dinner-partys-energetic-playlist-to-accompany-the-cover-3552669">策划了一个充满活力的播放列表</a>来配合他们的谈话。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-brits-announce-2024-rising-star-winner-3555457">《全英乐队宣布 2024 年新星获奖者》一文</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
格温妮丝·帕特洛还没有看过《复仇者联盟：终局之战》：“我在某个时候不再看漫威电影了” https://www.nme.com/news/film/gwyneth-paltrow-hasnt-seen-avengers-endgame-i-stopped-watching-marvel-movies-at-some-point-3555462?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=格温妮丝·帕特洛尚未看过《复仇者联盟》终局之战，我在某个时候停止观看漫威电影Adam StarkeyThu, 07 Dec 2023 18:55:54 +0000 Film NewsNewsMarvel Cinematic Universe https://www.nme.com/?p=3555462 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Gwyneth-Paltrow-main.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="格温妮丝·帕特洛" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Gwyneth-Paltrow-main.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Gwyneth-Paltrow-main-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Gwyneth-Paltrow-main-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Gwyneth-Paltrow-main-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Gwyneth-Paltrow-main-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Gwyneth-Paltrow-main-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我无法分辨谁是谁”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/gwyneth-paltrow-hasnt-seen-avengers-endgame-i-stopped-watching-marvel-movies-at-some-point-3555462">格温妮丝·帕特洛 (Gwyneth Paltrow) 没有看过《复仇者联盟：终局之战》：“我在某个时候不再看漫威电影了”的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Gwyneth-Paltrow-main.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="格温妮丝·帕特洛" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Gwyneth-Paltrow-main.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Gwyneth-Paltrow-main-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Gwyneth-Paltrow-main-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Gwyneth-Paltrow-main-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Gwyneth-Paltrow-main-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Gwyneth-Paltrow-main-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>格温妮丝·帕特洛表示，在她“在某个时候”停止观看漫威电影后，她仍然没有看过<em>《复仇者联盟：终局之战》</em> 。</p><p>这位在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/marvel-cinematic-universe">漫威电影宇宙</a>中扮演“小辣椒”的演员在沙特阿拉伯红海电影节的职业回顾演讲中解释了为什么她没有看过这部 2019 年超级英雄跨界大片。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/avengers-endgame-review-2479864#:~:text=In%20Endgame%20there%20is%20not,an%20epic%2C%20heartfelt%20thank%20you."><strong>《复仇者联盟：终局之战》评论：这是有史以来最好的漫画电影吗？</strong></a></li></ul><p>周三（12 月 6 日）在电影节上谈到漫威电影时（来自<a href="https://deadline.com/2023/12/gwyneth-paltrow-avengers-endgame-wes-anderson-paul-thomas-anderson-goop-red-sea-film-festival-1235655489/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Deadline</em></a> ），帕特洛说道：“说实话，我在某个时候就不再看它们了。我从来没有看过<em>《终局之战》</em> 。我无法追踪谁是谁。但也许在某个时候我应该这么做。”</p><p> 2008 年，帕特洛首次在漫威<em>电影</em>宇宙的第一部电影《钢铁<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robert-downey-jr">侠》中与小罗伯特·唐尼</a>演对手戏。与后来的漫威项目相比，帕特洛表示拍摄第一部<em>钢铁侠</em>“就像拍一部独立电影”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3555466" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3555466" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3555466" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Gwyneth-Paltrow-Robert-Downey-Jr-main.jpg" alt="格温妮丝·帕特洛 小罗伯特·唐尼" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Gwyneth-Paltrow-Robert-Downey-Jr-main.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Gwyneth-Paltrow-Robert-Downey-Jr-main-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Gwyneth-Paltrow-Robert-Downey-Jr-main-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Gwyneth-Paltrow-Robert-Downey-Jr-main-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Gwyneth-Paltrow-Robert-Downey-Jr-main-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Gwyneth-Paltrow-Robert-Downey-Jr-main-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3555466" class="wp-caption-text">格温妮丝·帕特洛和小罗伯特·唐尼 图片来源：Karwai Tang/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> “我们制作的第一部电影与其他电影非常不同，因为工作室认为它不会大受欢迎，”帕特洛说。 “他们聘请乔恩·费儒来执导谁是伟大的。他们还聘请了当时无法聘用的小罗伯特·唐尼。他的职业生涯正处于低谷。”</p><p>她补充道：“那部电影的几乎每个场景都是我们即兴创作的。我们会在早上在乔恩的预告片中写场景。这就像拍一部独立电影。后来这部电影大受欢迎，我们就不再那样拍了。”</p><p>除了在<em>《复仇者联盟：终局之战》</em>和 Netflix<em>连续剧《政客》</em>中露面外，帕特洛自 2017 年以来一直处于休息状态。过去几年，她一直在开发自己的健康品牌 Goop。</p><p>上个月，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/gwyneth-paltrow-retirement-3534233">帕特洛透露了一位可能让她复出的演员</a>。她在接受<em>《今夜娱乐》</em>采访时表示：“仅仅因为我的工作，目前我很难做好任何表演。</p><p> “但我想小罗伯特·唐尼可能总能把我找回来。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/gwyneth-paltrow-hasnt-seen-avengers-endgame-i-stopped-watching-marvel-movies-at-some-point-3555462">格温妮丝·帕特洛 (Gwyneth Paltrow) 没有看过《复仇者联盟：终局之战》：“我在某个时候不再看漫威电影了”的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
